        %h1 Solve Meaningful Problems With Software
        %h5 In nine months you will learn the technology, design, and business skills to launch a web application you care about.

    %section.what
      .inner
        %h2 What Is Starter School?
        %h5 Starter School is the grad school for people who want to learn how to build software and start companies. In a small class of highly motivated people, you will:
        %ol.steps-three.group
          %li
            %i.step-icon Step One
            %p Build the functional prototype of your web application by learning Ruby on Rails.
          %li
            %i.step-icon Step Two
            %p Make your app intuitive and beautiful with Web Design, HTML, CSS and Javascript.
          %li
            %i.step-icon Step Three
            %p Apply product development and business skills to ship your app and start a company.
        %a.button-more(href='#') Learn More

    %section.experts
      .inner.group
